For now,

Build libkitchensink from
$ git clone https://github.com/markmontymark/kitchen-sink.git
$ cd kitchen-sink
$ make

Build knr-c
$ git clone https://github.com/markmontymark/knr-c.git
$ cd knr-c
$ mkdir lib
$ cp ../kitchen-sink/lib/libkitchensink.so.1 lib
$ ln -s lib/libkitchensink.so.1 lib/libkitchensink.so
$ make 
